Source: univention-self-service
Section: univention
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Univention GmbH <packages@univention.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~),
 ucslint-univention,
 python2.7-dev,
 python-support,
 python-polib,
 univention-config-dev,
 univention-management-console-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.2
XS-Python-Version: 2.7


Package: univention-self-service-frontend
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 univention-config,
 ${misc:Depends},
 python-cherrypy3,
 libapache2-mod-wsgi
Description:
 This package contains the base modules for the UI of all univention self
 service frontend packages. It can be installed on all UCS server roles.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/


Package: univention-self-service-backend
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 univention-config,
 univention-join,
 shell-univention-lib,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description:
 This package contains the necessary configuration to use any of the
 Univention Self Services. It must be installed on the DC master and all DC
 backup servers that will serve as backends.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/


Package: univention-self-service-passwordreset-frontend
Architecture: all
Depends: univention-self-service-frontend,
 univention-config,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description:
 This package contains the password self service module that
 allows users to reset their password without administrator
 intervention. It can be installed on all UCS server roles.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/


Package: univention-management-console-module-passwordreset
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 univention-config,
 univention-postgresql,
 univention-postgresql-9.1,
 univention-join,
 shell-univention-lib,
 univention-apache,
 python-psycopg2,
 univention-self-service-backend,
 univention-mail-postfix | mail-transport-agent
Description:
 This package contains a UMC module that is the backend for the
 univention-self-service-passwordreset-frontend package. It that must be
 installed on a DC master or DC backup.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/


Package: univention-self-service-setpassword-frontend
Architecture: all
Depends: univention-self-service-frontend,
 univention-config,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description:
 This package contains the password self service module that
 allows users to change their own password. It can be installed
 on all UCS server roles.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/


Package: univention-self-service-setpassword-backend
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 univention-join,
 shell-univention-lib,
 univention-self-service-backend
Description:
 This package configures the backend for the
 univention-self-service-setpassword-frontend package.
 It that must be installed on a DC master and all DC
 backup servers that will serve as backends.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/


Package: univention-self-service-meta-singleserver
Architecture: all
Depends: univention-self-service-setpassword-backend,
 univention-self-service-setpassword-frontend,
 univention-management-console-module-passwordreset,
 univention-self-service-passwordreset-frontend
Description:
 This package installs all Univention Self Service modules on a DC master
 or DC backup.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/
